From: Rusty Russell <rusty@rustcorp.com.au>
References: 46872
Subject: put srcversion checksum in each modinfo section

Separate the module source and header checksum into a separate modinfo
field srcversion.  With CONFIG_MODULE_SRCVERSION_ALL=y, put srcversion
into every module, not just those with MODULE_VERSION("something").

Patch by Rusty Russell, trivial merging and testing by Matt Domsch.


